name: Prints by Shvembldr
description: In some of my NFTs where the image is generated per click, you can open the console (cmd or ctrl + i) and see the “seed”. This is the unique identifier of that particular image. You can get a high resolution 18x18 framed print of this image with my signature . To do this you will need: 1. Buy this NFT 2. Send me a PM on Twitter or Discord (shvembldr#2032) with number of the OBJKT, seed, and your wallet number (so I can verify that you bought it) and your address 3. Wait for the print to arrive
